ication**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18)\n   178→\n   179→## Iteration 9 — 2026-03-25T12:01:01Z — OK\n   180→- **Log**: iteration-009.log\n   181→\n   182→## Iteration 10 — 2026-03-25 — OK\n   183→\n   184→**Item**: [backend] `routes/referral.ts`: `GET /referral/stats` — referral summary stats endpoint\n   185→**Status**: Done\n   186→**Changes**:\n   187→- Added `GET /stats` endpoint to `services/backend/src/routes/referral.ts`\n   188→  - Requires JWT auth (wallet from context)\n   189→  - Calls `db.getReferralStats(wallet)` which returns snake_case `ReferralStats`\n   190→  - Maps to camelCase API response: `referredCount`, `activeCount`, `totalVolumeLamports`, `totalEarnedLamports`, `pendingLamports`\n   191→  - All monetary values are lamport strings (not floats)\n   192→  - Error handling: catches and logs failures, returns 500\n   193→  - Follows existing endpoint patterns (auth check, error shape, logger)\n   194→**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18)\n   195→\n   196→## Iteration 10 — 2026-03-25T12:03:21Z — OK\n   197→- **Log**: iteration-010.log\n   198→\n   199→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"92db3e41-1856-4eac-bac8-e2a98fa62710","uuid":"f5b0ee16-9112-4d84-b36e-4ae1d71b1408","timestamp":"2026-03-25T12:03:41.651Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/history.md","content":"# Implementation History — 300-referral-system\n\nIteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\nattempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\nof every iteration to understand prior context.\n\n---\n\n## Iteration 1 — 2026-03-24T21:27:27Z — OK\n\n**Item**: [backend] Database migration `011_referral.sql`\n**Status**: Done\n**Changes**:\n- Created `services/backend/migrations/011_referral.sql` with all 5 referral tables:\n  - `referral_codes` — one code per wallet (UNIQUE on wallet + code)\n  - `referral_links` — immutable referrer binding (UNIQUE on